        "timestamp": "2018-11-23 07:59:20.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Can you add a requirement.txt file listing package required, such\n > as tabulate.\n\nI don't think adding a requirement.txt is needed since this script is supposed to be usable as is. The tabulate module is used if available but is not mandatory",
